        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1200011291" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1200011291" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1200011291">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/dianne_du/">doudou</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-06-08</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">所谓世家家风，一曰知廉耻，一曰读诗书。口述者均出自出香门第，家族成员和姻亲故交中不乏近代史上的名人耆宿，将家族往事娓娓道来，谦逊朴实，有一说一。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
